| **csharp-lsp** | C# |
| **php-lsp** | PHP |
| **lua-lsp** | Lua |
""" ] ;
                            oc:sectionLevel 3 ;
                            oc:sectionOrder 5 ;
                            oc:sectionTitle "Language Servers (LSP)" ],
